OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Stan Ford
OL,5,FStan Ford, Age 99, Royal Navy
OL,7,FInterviewed 3 June 2023
OL,9,FManning a gun platform, Stan Ford was
OL,10,Fon board HMS Fratton - accompanying
OL,11,Fships taking men and supplies across
OL,12,Fthe Channel on D-Day.
OL,14,FIt was also a control vessel in the
OL,15,Flater effort to build an artificial
OL,16,Fharbour.
