OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Stan Ford
OL,5,F"When you are near explosions you
OL,6,Fdon't really hear them. You get a
OL,7,Ffeeling of disorientation.
OL,9,F"I was lucky I wasn't strapped in the
OL,10,Fgun.
OL,12,F"The gun platform and the gun and
OL,13,Fmyself - we went over the side
OL,14,Ftogether. Thank the Lord it saved me.
OL,15,FWeighed tonnes, it was all heavy
OL,16,Fmetal. And I came to the surface and
OL,17,Ffortunately we parted company as soon
OL,18,Fas we hit the water.
