OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Stan Ford
OL,5,FMr Ford suffers to this day from his
OL,6,Finjuries.
OL,8,F"I wear callipers on my legs. I
OL,9,Fsuffered a crushed fracture of the
OL,10,Fspine.
OL,12,F"It's something I am used to now."
